    "actor_description": "I don’t get it. I keep turning it over and it keeps coming back wrong. My brow tightens; I replay what I just saw or heard, hunting the missing step like it’s hiding in plain sight. The more I try to force it to click, the more it resists. I can feel my attention snagging—wait, how does that follow?—stuck at the point where the logic should bridge and doesn’t.",
    "description_text": "{actor} pauses, brow creasing as they look from one thing to another. Their head tilts, then stills; their eyes track as if trying to map an invisible route. They hover on the verge of speaking and stop again, caught between questions.",
